{
  "id": 6634466544058368,
  "name": "WebXR Layers",
  "summary": "WebXR Layers offers a more efficient way of drawing immersive content.\n\nIn addition to support for native color and depth textures and texture arrays, it also provides support for different layer types that are managed by the system compositor (as opposed to javascript).",
